reviewText: This movie seems cute but really it's pretty stupid. My 5 year old actually asked to turn it off and not watch it again. Only cost a couple of dollars, but still a waste of money and time.

A group of citified farm animals used to a star existence at a petting zoo try to adjust to their new environment when they\'re relocated to a dude ranch in these episodes of the offbeat animated series from Australia. The delightfully quirky characters include a business-savvy cow, a hip-hop-loving sheep, a gourmet-snob goat, a hip techno horse, an extreme-sports fan bull, a neurotic rat and an obsessive-compulsive crow.
